abstract_summ: Ten patients positive for SARS-CoV-2 nucleic acid detection by real time Reverse Transcription-Polymerase Chain Reaction (RT-PCR) were collected from The People's Hospital of Dazu District, Chongqing . The average age was 56.5 years (± 11.16), six patients were males, and the incubation period was 2–14 days . Dry cough was the main symptom, followed by fever and fatigue .
